::The Oblitercons/Scattershot/Punch::

The Oblitercons, save Dark One, all jump at the alarms, hearing Reptilica's 
message. Hiss grins. "Scavanger, Breakdown, you guys stay here in case they 
try to escape, me and Pyro will go get them."

Hiss and Pyro run off toward the torture chambers, leaving Scavanger and 
Breakdown guarding the door.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Scattershot and Punch hear Reptilica's message, both of them heading toward 
the tortrure chambers, a bit annoyed at the sirens.
